# Trivy ignore list. Auto-read from the repo root by `trivy image`/`trivy fs` on
# both CI hosts. Keep this list short and justified — every entry is a suppressed
# finding. Only add fixable HIGH/CRITICAL that are genuinely false positives or
# un-actionable; never suppress to silence a real, fixable vulnerability.

# --- Firefox bundled expat (desktop image only) ------------------------------
# Reported against the Mozilla-PPA firefox .deb because Trivy's "fixed version"
# points at the *snap* build (which this image deliberately avoids). The image
# ships current (2026) firefox; these are 2022 expat CVEs long since patched
# upstream. Not present in backend/frontend (no firefox there), so scoping here
# is effectively desktop-only.
CVE-2022-25235
CVE-2022-25236
